<p>our relations shall be. I hear that he has started the course on economics about which he spoke to me &amp; which caused the outspoken advice of mine which he disliked. I think I shall go back to a hospital when the "scheme" is in full working order, for then there will be no reason why I should stay with the unit longer, &amp; I can then get to work in earnest.</p>
<p>My present necessity is to overcome a very strong disinclination to work, &amp; get on with any shorthand &amp; English on very possible opportunity.</p>
